{"tid":167664,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"到底所謂係寫字樓工作即係有咩再做？","createTime":"2017-03-23T04:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T03:22:58.000Z","uid":75033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4fbc5be34c308c3d73c43bcbc24e6f3c323058","tid":167664,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:03:04.000Z","msg":"仲讀緊書未畢業 冇工作經驗 <br />\n認真想知出左黎做野既巴絲 你係公司係要做啲咩？<br />\n唔計會計呢啲要牌考牌或者叫做專業小小既工作<br />\n如果讀management/ marketing / econ / finance 呢啲grad既人係有咩工作做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該咁講 如果我係management grad 我一開始通常係有咩工作做？ 同埋大公司同細公司係delegate 工作比你方面會唔會好大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原諒我無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653fe766d9df1f8568cedcaaa221d30c25d011d8","tid":167664,"uid":42221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"影印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出下email咁"},{"pid":"d48e2b58d5acd098f8d2aaa36423bb45155e38c4","tid":167664,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"Topic 即係有咩要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2237c0fad2cdace9df106a71bd5637cb493eab30","tid":167664,"uid":60404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"做狗"},{"pid":"916b9586e520f4716865afa426664f605efd0c3d","tid":167664,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出下email咁</blockquote><br />\n巴打開始做野幾耐？ 影印出email呢類型工作維持左幾耐？ 真心想知其實會唔會覺得淨係做呢類野根本係冇得上位？"},{"pid":"fc0bac4211a7894889951ba891ec89f5b823df14","tid":167664,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"283400857f6a6383eeb9661791be9fb